title: Snowboarding at Billabong Attack 2013 Japan
description:
Billabong team rider, Yoh Tanaka takes out the 2013 Billabong Attack presented by Xperia!

On Sunday the 31st of March 2013, Japan's largest straight jump snowboarding event, the Billabong Attack presented by Xperia provided some of the best snowboarding seen to date in Japan
